title: ROB AND BAND REHEARSE FOR UPCOMING BI-COASTAL MELALI TOUR
description:
Rob and the Melali Sessions Band let us into the studio as they prepare for the Melali: The Drifter Sessions tour, scheduled to kick off in Solana Beach, California at Belly Up Tavern. 

Video: PK
